subject: Out of Office RE: FW: FW: Flock - Evidence.com integration
body:
[EXTERNAL ?]

Hello,

Thank you for reaching out. I am currently out of office from Tuesday,
5/13- Sunday 5/18 but I have you covered! Please see below for who to
reach out to:

If you are in need of immediate assistance in Washington, Oregon, or
Idaho, please reach out to your newly introduced CSM,
gaby.mahoney@flocksafety.com.

For immediate assistance in California, please reach out to your
previous CSM, libby.landers@flocksafety.com or
kyle.turner@flocksafety.com.

If this is a "how to use the software" or any other technical-related
question?, please contact our support team at support@flocksafety.com.

If you have a billing question or invoice question, please email
billing@flocksafety.com

If this is related to your remaining installations, please contact
your project manager. If you do not remember who your project manager
is, you can reach out to support@flocksafety.com and they should be
able to assist.

I�ll be in touch as soon as possible. Thank you for being so patient
and have a great week!

Best,
Emily


--


Emily Atzen
Customer Success Manager
